* Welcome to the Super-power Handbook *

We are glad for your interest in unleashing your potential.  This
material is designed to give you  tips that will help you get the most
out of your life.  After all, you've only got one.  Make the most of
it. There are no do-overs.

You can enjoy this material in three different ways.  Each of these
are optimized for busy people.  We know that you have a ton of things
competing for your attention.  So we have provided multiple
formats. Pick the one that works best for you.


**Web Site**

The web site contains all of the information and uses links to help
you jump around through related topics.  This is great for people who
like to follow their own path.  [[http://shrinking-world.org][Web Site]]


**Email Articles**

You can sign up to get an article each week delivered free of charge
to your email account.  Each email has a short intro.  If you are
interested in the article you can read it on the web site.  Cancel
anytime that you lose interest.  [[http://shrinking-world.org/media/forms/signup.html][Sign Up]]


**Kindle Book**

This content will also be available soon as a Kindle book.  If you are
interested in this then email me.  If I get enough queries it will
speed up the release date.  [[http://amazon.com][Web Site]]

